title: #92Noon! Vikings & Border Battle Blowout
description: Disastrous loss is the theme of the Tuesday's show, with a montage, calls, talkers and more, related to last night's Vikings loss. Sinykin adds his victory smug as well. Most importantly, Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays to all of you for listening to #92Noon. We love you for it.
